%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

is_basic_infertility_service(diagnose_and_evaluate_underlying_medical_cause_of_infertility)
